::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Take it easy. If there's an issue, we can sit down and discuss it...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501027151-->
:::'''Chavez:''' Huh? What are you talking about?
:::'''Chavez:''' ...You misunderstood what I meant! All we want is to make Lady Bronya aware of the Dark-Blue Scam. This issue has implications for the peace and stability of Belobog.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_501027153-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501027153-->
::'''Chavez:''' I heard that the Supreme Guardian Lady Bronya is far more open-minded than the former Supreme Guardian. She is encouraging people at Qlipoth Fort to air their opinions. Everyone has a responsibility to speak... Well, the Dark-Blue Scam Victims Association naturally isn't going to let this opportunity get away.
::'''Chavez:''' Our request is quite simple. The Silvermane Guards should immediately establish a Dark-Blue Scam Special Task Force that will launch a city-wide search in Belobog to round up this blue-haired con artist...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What will happen after the task force catches him?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501027156-->
:::'''Chavez:''' That's easy. They should tie this wretched villain up and lock him beneath Qlipoth Fort to be questioned under torture. The interrogation would continue until he has confessed all of his crimes. After that, he'll be hanged outside the city...
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} ...That's ambitious.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501027158-->
